This is a Simple Restaurant Website with a main home page, types of food available, a food menu, customer reviews, and a contact form section on the restaurant website.An online restaurant website is a digital version of any restaurant that allows users to order food directly from the restaurant while sitting at home.

projects.name: Sanket(Sign Language Conversion)
projects.description: The proposed sign language conversion system consists of several key modules that work together to convert sign language gestures into sign language glosses,which are the written or spoken representations of sign language.The main modules in the system are: Data Acquisition Module,Pre-processing Module,Feature Extraction Module,Sign language Gloss Conversion Module,User Interface Module,Temporal Modelling Module.
